snippet.title: Blood Bar Tycoon - Launch Trailer
snippet.description:
Wishlist Blood Bar Tycoon on Steam now!
🔗https://store.steampowered.com/app/2776780/Blood_Bar_Tycoon?utm_source=youtube&utm_medium=launchTrailer

🦇 Become the ultimate vampire bar manager in Blood Bar Tycoon! 🧛‍♂️ Enhance your bars, lure the tastiest humans from the neighborhood, dodge unfortunate incidents, accumulate wealth, and ascend to power in Crimson City alongside the Elders! 💰

Crafted with passion by a team of Belgian game developers! 🎮
